data.description:
Explore this exceptional Forney residence located in the prestigious Rockwall Independent School District! This meticulously maintained 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem showcases a harmonious blend of elegance and functionality.

Step inside to discover an inviting open layout seamlessly connecting the kitchen, living room, and dining area. The kitchen is a delightful combination of sophistication and practicality, creating an ideal space for effortless cooking. The living room features a charming fireplace, perfect for cozy gatherings. The master bedroom boasts a private bathroom, providing a serene retreat.

Enjoy proximity to Lake Ray Hubbard with convenient boat ramp access, and rest assured knowing your children will attend the highly regarded Rockwall ISD. Don't miss this opportunity to secure a remarkable home!

Explore the option of third-party seller financing—call now for more details and to seize this incredible opportunity!
